beer.beer_description: A juicy hop bomb in a hazy base. Brewed exclusively with a new form of super concentrated lupulin powder, the product of a cryogenic extraction process which separates aromatic resins and oils from hop plant matter. The green gold powder produced gives this beer a massive, mellow, juicy hop hit with none of the harsh kick of vegetative cone material. So kick off your shoes, relax your feet and crack open a can of this lupulin treat.
